Recommends: gnome-terminal
Description: BCV and Binance P2P exchange rates in the GNOME top bar
 lazyrate shows the official BCV exchange rate and the Binance P2P
 (USDT/VES) market rate for Venezuela directly in the GNOME top bar
 through an AppIndicator, and provides a lazydocker-style terminal
 user interface with history, statistics and charts.
 .
 The TUI stack (textual, textual-plotext and their dependencies) is
 vendored under /usr/lib/lazyrate because the versions packaged in
 the Ubuntu archive are too old or missing. Rates are fetched on a
 schedule, stored locally in SQLite and displayed with day change,
 trend and gap between both sources.
